Document: PhysicsDirectSpaceState3D
Path: godot/classes/class_physicsdirectspacestate3d.rst
Summary: Provides direct access to a physics space in the PhysicsServer3D, used for queries against objects and areas.

Note: This class is not meant to be instantiated directly. Use World3D.direct_space_state to get the world's physics 3D space state.
